data.description: Casual elegance in this beautiful ranch style home on tree lined street. Remodeled kitchen with microwave/convection oven, cherry finish slow close cabinets, corian countertops with recessed sink, & seeded glass cabinet. Upgraded kitchen flooring. Remodeled main bath. Large laundry room with built in ironing board. Large airy rec room with large windows & great view of fenced yard. Custom window treatments, hardwood floors, 30 year roof tile, basement bar and more! Why move to Valparaiso? Fantastic green spaces-over 20 dog parks, trails, skate park, golf parks & numerous neighborhood parks. Low, low Porter county taxes & cost of living. "A" rated Valparaiso elementary middle & high schools. Close to bustling downtown picturesque Valparaiso which is home to the famous Popcorn Festival & the Porter County Fair. Excellent amenities like shopping, dining & nightlife. A feeling of safety & security. Valparaiso is close to major highways that allow easy access to surrounding major cities.
